{"tid":1641000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【自發經濟援助】我係一名被起訴人士，我想瘋狂請朋友食飯","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:50:04.000Z","uid":258236,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"92051e58640148247f3606daae03e5382b31d8ac","tid":1641000,"uid":258236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無錢買零食？搵啊源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢買禦寒衣物？搵啊源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢買文具？搵啊源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbWc3Tv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbWc3Tv.jpg&h=c305b83e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我叫啊源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢幾個月被落案起訴既人其中之一<br />\n自從被起訴之後，我十分空閒又寂寞，於是決定係連登呢個地方招朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">源起</span><br />\n最近係網上見到好多傳聞，係香港呢個咁富裕既社會竟然有好多人有三餐不繼既問題，或者出現各種各樣既財政困難。我好擔心佢地，唔想佢地既連基本生活都負擔唔到。同時，我知道香港有好多有錢既家長，好有心想資助佢地既生活，但係苦無渠道，又驚俾人呃錢，甚至開始捉鬼互屌。我唔想呢種情況繼續落去，而啊源都叫有個被捕被起訴既光環，希望呢個身分可以令大家信我唔係鬼，資助我請我既朋友食飯，同佢地聯誼。<br />\n<br />\n因此，請各位家長留意，啊源係專注認識<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有即時經濟需要</strong></span></span>既朋友。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我想請 frd 子食飯呀！！！</span><br />\n我係一個對朋友好大方既人，無論係咪好熟既朋友都好，我都好鐘意俾錢請佢食飯、俾錢請佢買衫等等。我對朋友好好，希望大家都肯同我做朋友！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請有意同啊源做frd子既朋友，下載Wire 呢個app，加我做朋友：ahyuen</span></span></strong><br />\n大家互相了解之後，啊源會決定同唔同你做朋友，請唔請你食飯（通常都請）。<br />\n招frd 子要求<br />\n啊源雖然想廣交眾友，但都唔係濫交架！我好小學雞，對朋友會有以下條件：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1）黃絲，藍絲免問<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2）有即時經濟需要</span><br />\n3）相信我，唔介意同我分享你既故事</span></strong><br />\n到時搵我傾偈既時候，可能我會要求你影d同你有關既照片，希望你唔好介意，唔係惡意而係保障大家！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尋求家長資助</span><br />\n睇完上文都知道啊源會係一個好大洗既人，好想有好家長可以支持我呢種揮霍既生活模式。我毒撚一個，無咩洗費要用，淨係我同朋友聯誼果方面要用好多錢，希望可以睇在我年少輕狂份上，俾多d零用錢我洗！<br />\n想做金主既家長，不論金額大小，我都希望你向我同我既朋友付出一d心意，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用Telegram 金主聯絡熱線，會話俾你知資助啊源既方法：lihkg_yuen</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點樣保障大家？</span><br />\n我好重視我既朋友，雖然我有好多朋友，但係我好口密。我得到既任何個人資料，包括用户 名、銀行户口、全名等等，只會經過啊源一個人既手，絕對唔會有第三者或任何義工得到，請放心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啊源好驚網上d 木馬病毒，所以正採用最高保密既設備。而且我電話無咩容量，惟有好勤力剷圖剷紀錄。萬一啊源有咩不測，都唔可以累到各方好友。<br />\n啊源唔會對外招收任何義工，以防止任何被滲透既可能。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">財富管理方面</span><br />\n雖然啊源又大洗又窮，但係對於自己既財富管理係好有計劃架！平時使左幾多錢，係會逐條逐條數寫低既。啊源份人好善忘，惟有好蠢咁整個spreadsheet 俾自己睇，等我記得我既日常開支，亦都順便俾好心資助我既家長，睇返我既洗費記錄呀！我會起碼每2-3日更新一次呢個紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Disclaimer</span><br />\n家長們可能會擔心啊源把關不足，而令金錢被濫用。<br />\n我可以肯定話俾家長知，當中必定會有被濫用既成分，畢竟鬼呢樣野防不勝防，我話我防到全部鬼你都唔信啦。<br />\n我必須承認，有部分既金錢有機會會俾鬼呃左去，但係啊源會盡力把關，包括問新朋友拎相去證明、有懷疑個案或大額個案會特別查證等等，希望大家明白同理解。<br />\n如果家長接受到會有小部分被濫用既呢個狀況，而又信得過啊源，就請課金支持，感謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FAQ</span><br />\nQ: 你既意思係咪 612 同 星火 信唔過先？<br />\nA: 唔係，啊源自己都有受過612 基金既幫助，佢地好好，唔麻煩亦好有心好快手。我自己都好感激佢地既經濟援助。我個人認為佢地係被過分追擊，有被抹黑既可能，希望大家俾多d信任。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁點解要另起爐灶啊？<br />\nA: 其實現時啊源係集中想處理有即時經濟需要既frd 子，同612基金既定位並唔同，亦都希望減輕其他基金既工作負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解要信你呀？<br />\nA: 我惟一可以用既光環就係曾經被捕被起訴呢樣野，希望呢樣野可以證明我唔係鬼。至於其他實行上既野，除左最後既財富管理報表之外，我都不便太詳細去透露。只能夠同大家講我已經做左一段時間既research，去確保成個運作既保密同安全，去到呢個位惟有講個信字。但我可以話，新frd 子同埋家長既安全係我放係第一位既野，即使我或者我既幫手被刮到，都唔會令大家既資料輕易洩露。<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩問題、意見同建議既話歡迎留言。<br />\n如果你認為啊源呢個方法可行，請幫我推post 同正皮，因為啊源唔會得閒推post 了，謝謝。"},{"pid":"6322e3758e0c7db0c0bc618cc480bf39cb613b57","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77a6bd8d0e42db71be70d19576f7d7c3646d9daa","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b943dcb0e964b8e4cd4734c56d60b9168b34ec0","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c13ad5c168d8fa6b1b65506c17e07f5c426399d","tid":1641000,"uid":258236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d3736dc557e6fd4cf76231ee79e7dbe1fb10f25","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ae7ced7db0f52c748dc865719f0d1cebf73f0f8","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f14501ee0f584bda52c642c4cc72f565b244ea0","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e9ad6daff674ba0fb0aab0c2a9bf16b5d309e5d","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed804d427d4ad185837e7edff6561b3d4399ad2","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d556ce934237c227edcd7ac49b2b97d73f78c103","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a3f0c40f80e282111905142c240474a8fe5b74b","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70053b9b105fb4b87b0c793ee6ae48edb2cc6fb2","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3b27a0cdd99cb73008ce9c64e62801c03a8fb5e","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"768f03f21e92f317b16a43d6f60e746bb0c2a997","tid":1641000,"uid":230391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad0c4c3f672c6506c08b42f4aaa7fb7fc9c957e6","tid":1641000,"uid":216044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f439addedb478485eb452a2b30129c69e1a7da20","tid":1641000,"uid":258236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dfb9c89ed905882a86083fbce4ccabb0b058fbd","tid":1641000,"uid":18473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"可能我會要求你影d同你有關既照片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793dda0e0b953d7d4fd616faf39c514503d163cc","tid":1641000,"uid":1673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"幫你推啦"},{"pid":"3fe318099ca909931f910f73fa6bcc3bf7846b90","tid":1641000,"uid":262966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216dc6b2806fdb4717ae2aa91d834311b8e7079d","tid":1641000,"uid":250027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78bcd6eba812816a30f67af5a9389f81dbda0e3","tid":1641000,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afc9158473d819b670e15d81b2e830134d2bcb12","tid":1641000,"uid":1646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"要現身仲要比影相，其實好令人卻步<br />\n<br />\n諗下辦法係唔洗見面既網上商店啦e.g. HKTV"},{"pid":"db373c8e217cf112c393c53f66b4a4ead9cdc7b1","tid":1641000,"uid":106933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"起底 又話自己係中學生 邊黎咁多錢請人? 要保護人仲會叫人同你講發夢?俾你影相 俾個人資料你? <br />\n狗就可以輕易扮被捕過 要咩資料一定齊又最清楚<br />\n不可信 大家小心 <br />\n不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786ae9940946bcf99da097364f7697a13b0063ce","tid":1641000,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"push"}]}